acceptance_criteria: templates-save contract schema and wrapper only expose/emit flags accepted by pm templates save --help; regression tests cover schema and arg building.
parent: pm-o7be
reporter: codex-agent
severity: high
environment: cli
repro_steps: Inspect contracts templates-save branch and run templates save with createMode.
resolution: Filtered templates-save schema/arg mappings to supported flags so Pi wrapper no longer emits unsupported CLI options.
expected_result: Contracted wrapper parameters map to valid CLI flags.
actual_result: Wrapper emits unsupported flags and CLI returns unknown_option.
component: pi-wrapper-contracts
regression: true
customer_impact: Agent tool invocations can fail despite passing schema validation.
comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-25T20:01:16.224Z",codex-agent,"Duplicate-check evidence: pm context --limit 10; pm search 'templates save create-mode contracts mismatch' --limit 10; pm list-open --limit 20; pm list-in-progress --limit 20. Net-new because no active item tracked templates-save createMode/schema parity bug."
  "2026-04-25T20:03:46.240Z",codex-agent,"Constrained templates-save schema/wrapper options to supported flags only; removed createMode/schedulePreset/unset/clear* from templates-save action contract and arg emission. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/pi-agent-extension.spec.ts (11 passed)."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-25T20:01:16.224Z",codex-agent,Mismatch observed between pm contracts action schema and templates command help/options.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-25T20:01:16.224Z",codex-agent,"Action schema contracts must be constrained per subcommand support,not inherited wholesale from create."
